# Line endings: this repo's .editorconfig mandates `end_of_line = crlf` for all files, and the
# analyzers enforce it (IDE0055). Blobs are stored normalized to LF; force a CRLF working tree on
# checkout on EVERY platform so the analyzer passes on Linux CI, not only on Windows (where autocrlf
# happened to hide it). Without this, a fresh Linux checkout gets LF working files and IDE0055 fails.
* text=auto eol=crlf
